		?<br>
		<div class="header3">2004 JCP Awards Ceremony</div>
		<div class="header4">The JCP Program Praises Excellence Within the Java Community</div>
		<em>By Susan Mitchell</em><br>
		&nbsp;<br>
		  <div></div> <!-- NS4 Font Fix //-->
		  
